    <BlogCrossLinks title="Top Bingo Stems: SATIRE and Beyond — The Ultimate Bingo Reference" />

    <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
      <time datetime="2026-06-15">June 15, 2026</time>
      <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600"></span>
      <span>8 min read</span>
    </div>

    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">A bingo stem is a 6-letter combination that produces an unusually high number of valid 7-letter words. Memorising just the top 10 stems dramatically increases your bingo frequency — and SATIRE sits unchallenged at the top of the list with over 66 playable bingos.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Why SATIRE Dominates</h2>

    <p>The letters S-A-T-I-R-E combine the most common consonants (S, T, R) with the most common vowels (A, I, E). This frequency alignment means nearly every additional letter you draw creates a valid 7-letter word.</p>

    <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Key Insight</p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-200">SATIRE produces bingos with <span class="text-white font-medium">23 of the 26 possible added letters</span>. Only Q, X, and Z fail to complete a valid word in TWL — and even Z works in SOWPODS with certain arrangements.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
      <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <thead class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">+ Letter</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Bingo(s)</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Score</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-800">
          <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3">+ B</td><td class="px-4 py-3">BAITERS, REBAITS</td><td class="px-4 py-3">59</td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3">+ C</td><td class="px-4 py-3">RACIEST, STEARIC</td><td class="px-4 py-3">59</td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3">+ D</td><td class="px-4 py-3">TIRADES, STAIDER, DISRATE</td><td class="px-4 py-3">58</td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3">+ G</td><td class="px-4 py-3">STAGIER, GAITERS, TRIAGES</td><td class="px-4 py-3">58</td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3">+ L</td><td class="px-4 py-3">REALIST, SALTIER, RETAILS</td><td class="px-4 py-3">57</td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3">+ N</td><td class="px-4 py-3">NASTIER, RETINAS, RETAINS</td><td class="px-4 py-3">57</td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3">+ P</td><td class="px-4 py-3">PARTIES, PASTIER, PIRATES</td><td class="px-4 py-3">59</td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3">+ W</td><td class="px-4 py-3">WAITERS, WARIEST, WASTIER</td><td class="px-4 py-3">60</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">The Top 10 Bingo Stems Ranked</h2>

    <p>While SATIRE leads, the next nine stems are all within striking distance. Memorising all ten gives you coverage of over 500 potential bingos.</p>

