          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Scan for partial stems</span> — With 5 of 6 stem letters, sacrifice 5-10 points to keep the partial and draw into it</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">2</span>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Leave management</span> — After playing a word, check if your remaining tiles form part of a top stem</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">3</span>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Recognize anagrams</span> — SATIRE rearranges to AIREST, TERAIS, etc. Spot it regardless of order</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">4</span>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Combine with hooks</span> — Know which board positions allow 7-letter plays parallel to existing words</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">5</span>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Apply the 2-turn rule</span> — If you haven't completed the stem in 2 turns of low scoring, abandon and play your best word</p>
        </div>
