    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Stem Overlap and Multi-Stem Racks</h2>

    <p>The most powerful racks contain letters from multiple top stems simultaneously. For example, SATIREN contains both SATIRE (+N) and RETAIN (+S) — giving you multiple bingo paths regardless of your 7th tile.</p>

    <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
        <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✓ Multi-Stem Rack</p>
