      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-500/30 bg-red-950/10">
        <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✗ Single-Stem Tunnel Vision</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Holding SATIR and waiting 3+ turns for E. Better to play and reset after 2 failed draws.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
